    <item>
      <title>斯塔默称创造财富是工党的“首要任务”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/starmer-says-wealth-creation-is-labour-s-number-one-mission</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 称赞英国创造财富是工党的“首要任务”，工党在民调中领先的地位将继续努力在 7 月 4 日大选之前争取企业和中产阶级选民的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/starmer-says-wealth-creation-is-labour-s-number-one-mission</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 08:36:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称新的加沙停火提议是“决定性时刻”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-raises-pressure-on-israel-hamas-for-deal-to-end-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国表示，新的停火提议将使以色列和哈马斯之间的战斗暂停至少六周，这可能标志着冲突的“决定性时刻”——如果双方在几次和平尝试失败后达成一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-raises-pressure-on-israel-hamas-for-deal-to-end-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 18:22:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
